rComments: This prof is a very though grader. He is very particular, especially with spelling and grammar. An intimidating man, not very open or nice. When you ask for help, he does nothing but tell you that you were wrong and he's right, often giving no explanation of why you lost points.
Ok teacher, he is so passionate about art that you can't help but listen to him. Kind of monotonous though; which sometimes makes it hard to stay awake.
He knows a lot about curating and art history but thinks fine art is a superior discipline.  A little snobby.

Awsome teacher, sometimes searching for the exact words (giving us time to write stuff down), like the other said, cute in a certain way, friendly, if you listened in class you should have a good grade.  We miss him!!!
Great prof, but very soft spoken, kind of cute in a weird funny way. covers a lot of stuff in the course, marks tests/proposal easy, but final essay is worth about 60% of grade. eek!
